"2 cups uncooked penne (tube-shaped) pasta","2 cups (1-inch) cut green beans (about 1/2 pound)","2 cups shredded cooked chicken breast","1/2 cup vertically sliced red onion","1/4 cup chopped fresh basil","1 1/2 teaspoons chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1  (7-ounce) bottle roasted red bell pepper, drained and cut into thin strips","2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","1 tablespoon cold water","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon bottled minced garlic","1/4 teaspoon black pepper"